Package com.facebook.openwifi.rrm.optimizers.channel

Class RandomChannelInitializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.openwifi.rrm.optimizers.channel.ChannelOptimizer
      • com.facebook.openwifi.rrm.optimizers.channel.RandomChannelInitializer
  • public class RandomChannelInitializer
extends ChannelOptimizer
    Random channel initializer.

    Randomly assign APs to the same channel unless otherwise specified. If specified, all APs will be assigned a random channel.
